metadata.name: 8 Ball Nifty Club (8BNC)
metadata.description:
Yo, listen up! Get ready to join the 8 Ball Nifty Club, the hottest NFT project out there! We've got 8888 unique NFTs that are straight-up fire, representing dope characters for our Billard Web3 game.

These NFTs are the real deal, with sick visuals and details that'll have you shook. And what's even better? As a member of our club, you'll be part of a tight-knit community of collectors and enthusiasts who are just as passionate about billiards as you are.

Don't sleep on this opportunity to own a piece of history and show off your swag with one of our 8 Ball Nifty Club NFTs. Whether you're a seasoned collector or new to the game, we've got something for everyone. So don't wait, cop your NFT today and join the club!
